      " TASK 2: Inference Rules\n",
      "============================================================\n",
      "\n",
      " MODUS PONENS\n",
      "----------------------------------------\n",
      " Premise 1 (P) : Ahmed has Speed_Above_Limit = True\n",
      " Premise 2 (P→Q) : Speed_Above_Limit Challan_Issued\n",
      " Conclusion (Q) : Challan_Issued\n",
      " Logical Notation : P, P→Q ⊢ Q\n",
      " Python Result : Is Challan Issued? → YES \n",
